{"tid":1276121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港示威者衝擊立會　特朗普：他們都是為了追求民主","createTime":"2019-07-02T01:33:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T02:20:40.000Z","uid":20933,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7da5e875141b12488f6803ba864c86879451e2","tid":1276121,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:33:10.000Z","msg":"修訂《逃犯條例》風波持續發酵，有示威者趁昨日（1日）將行動升級，衝擊並一度佔領立法會大樓。美國總統特朗普回應衝擊時，對香港動蕩感到哀傷，形容示威者為追求民主的一群人。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱：「他們都是為了追求民主，而我想大部分人都是希望擁有民主，不過可惜的是，有些政府不想有民主。」 <br />\n<br />\n另外，美國眾議院議長佩洛西則在Twitter發帖，表示香港人在過去數周站起來反抗修訂《逃犯條例》的行徑，啟迪了世人，強調不論二十國集團（G20）成員還是其他國家，都不應該無視港人的勇氣。"},{"pid":"52990d068426b6dd7417c7a7df5c564ec50c57de","tid":1276121,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:33:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190702/s00001/1562026543926/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190702%2Fs00001%2F1562026543926%2F&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=5f8e0b01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190702%2Fs00001%2F1562026543926%2F&h=a7420b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190702/s00001/1562026543926/</a>"},{"pid":"bb929625603eafd6fa8543514e3ad0081b0236ed","tid":1276121,"uid":196712,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:33:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a90cd2ad0a61b298541a557522f1ea7788b50f2b","tid":1276121,"uid":157793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:34:13.000Z","msg":"香港加油，特朗普都加油！"},{"pid":"d0c1e2300e3b28948ee81e240e7c41f7f738118b","tid":1276121,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"香港民主人權法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nthis way sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/l